text: Sayoko Kitabatake is an archer from Japan. She was born on 24 October 1978. Kitabatake competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics, 2004 Summer Olympics, and 2008 Summer Olympics.Sayoko Kawauchi-KitabatakeSayoko KAWAUCHI == References == Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese archers Category:Olympians for Japan
